'''ᱠᱷᱚᱭ''' (ᱟᱨ ᱵᱟᱝ '''''ᱞᱤᱭᱟ''''') ᱫᱚ ᱦᱳᱲᱳ ᱠᱚ ᱟᱨᱟ ᱞᱮᱠᱷᱟᱱ ᱛᱮᱭᱟᱨᱚᱜᱻᱟ ।<ref>{{cite book|last=Ray|first=Dr. Krishna Gopal|title=Volume 5 of Fairs and Festivals of India|year=2003|publisher=Gyan Pub. House|isbn=9788121205894|pages=471|url=http://books.google.co.in/books?id=JQjgAAAAMAAJ&q=lia+ukhuda+orissa&dq=lia+ukhuda+orissa&hl=en&sa=X&ei=_ZZtT5b7C8TrrQflmtCgDg&redir_esc=y}}</ref><ref name=khai>{{cite book|last=Das, Patnaik|first=Raicharan, Dhirendranath|title=Festivals of Orissa|year=1982|publisher=Orissa Sahitya Akademi|pages=80|url=http://books.google.co.in/books?id=a9PQAAAAMAAJ&q=lia+ukhuda+orissa&dq=lia+ukhuda+orissa&hl=en&sa=X&ei=_ZZtT5b7C8TrrQflmtCgDg&redir_esc=y}}</ref>) ᱱᱚᱶᱟ [[ᱳᱰᱤᱥᱟ] ᱨᱮ ᱡᱟ.ᱥᱛᱤ ᱠᱚ ᱡᱚᱢᱻᱟ ।<ref name=pakhala>{{cite book|last=Panda|first=Shishir Kumar|title=Medieval Orissa: a socio-economic study|year=1991|publisher=Mittal Publications|isbn=9788170992615|pages=152|url=http://books.google.co.in/books?id=C_LT5Q-f3YEC&lpg=PA94&dq=pakhala%20orissa&pg=PA94#v=onepage&q=pakhala%20orissa&f=false}}</ref> ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱫᱚ '''ᱞᱤᱭᱟ''' ᱦᱚᱸ ᱠᱚ ᱢᱮᱨᱟᱜ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾ ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱛᱮᱭᱟᱨᱚᱜ ᱠᱚ ᱟᱨ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱡᱚᱢᱟᱜ ᱫᱚ [[ᱩᱠᱷᱩᱰᱟ]] ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ।<ref>{{cite book|last=Jena|first=B. B.|title=Orissa, people, culture, and polity|year=1980|publisher=Kalyani Publishers, Original from the University of Michigan|url=http://books.google.co.in/books?id=4zNuAAAAMAAJ&q=lia+ukhuda+orissa&dq=lia+ukhuda+orissa&hl=en&sa=X&ei=_ZZtT5b7C8TrrQflmtCgDg&redir_esc=y}}</ref> [[ᱠᱳᱨᱟᱠᱷᱚᱭᱤ]] ᱫᱚ [[ᱞᱤᱝᱜᱚᱨᱟᱡᱽ]]ᱻᱟᱜ ᱵᱷᱳᱜᱽ ᱨᱮ ᱠᱚ ᱪᱟᱞ ᱟᱭᱟ ᱾<ref>[http://khordha.nic.in/lingaraj/lingaraj.htm Lord Lingaraja, Offerings]</ref>

==ᱠᱷᱚᱭ ᱪᱟᱞᱟ==
ᱦᱟᱥᱟ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱴᱩᱠᱩᱡ ᱨᱮ ᱵᱟ.ᱞᱤ ᱠᱚ ᱞᱚᱞᱚ ᱭᱟ ᱾ ᱛᱮ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱨᱮ [[ᱦᱳᱲᱳ]] ᱠᱚ ᱠᱷᱟᱸᱡᱚᱭᱟ ᱾ ᱦᱳᱲᱳ ᱚᱴᱮᱡ ᱞᱮᱱ ᱠᱷᱟᱱ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱠᱷᱚᱭ ᱟᱨ ᱵᱟᱝ ᱞᱤᱭᱟ ᱵᱮᱱᱟᱜᱻᱟ ᱾ ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱠᱷᱚᱭ ᱥᱟᱝ ᱫᱚ ᱦᱳᱲᱳ ᱪᱚᱠᱟᱜ ᱞᱟᱴᱷᱟ ᱠᱚᱜ ᱜᱮᱭᱟ ᱛᱚᱵᱮ ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱠᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱪᱟᱞᱟ ᱛᱮ ᱠᱚ ᱪᱟᱞᱟᱭᱟ ᱾ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱜᱮ ᱠᱷᱚᱭ ᱪᱟᱞᱟ ᱫᱚ ᱠᱚ ᱧᱩᱢ ᱟᱫ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾ ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱫᱚ ᱢᱟᱫ ᱦᱩᱥᱤᱫ ᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱠᱚ ᱵᱮᱱᱟᱣᱻᱟ ᱾

